tty_images/1705145695/image_1705145695.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705145695/image_1705145695.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705145695/image_1705145695.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705145695/image_1705145695.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705145695/image_1705145695.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705145695/image_1705145695.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705145695/image_1705145695.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">David Gyung</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The<strong> JPMorgan Equity Premium Income ETF</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/JEPI\" title=\"JPMorgan Equity Premium Income ETF\">JEPI</a></span>) is an exchange-traded fund which seeks to capitalize from long-term appreciation of the stock market while also offering a generous monthly dividend yield. In theory, if executed well, this could</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705145695/image_1705145695.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742870-jepi-macroeconomic-volatility-could-help-performance-in-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 14:30:25"}, {"id": "4742868", "title": "Salesforce Is Fairly Valued Now (Rating Downgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161221488/image_2161221488.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Artificial Intelligence Machine Learning Large Language Model Technology\" data-id=\"2161221488\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"960px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161221488/image_2161221488.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161221488/image_2161221488.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161221488/image_2161221488.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161221488/image_2161221488.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161221488/image_2161221488.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161221488/image_2161221488.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161221488/image_2161221488.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161221488/image_2161221488.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Just_Super/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Shares of Salesforce (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CRM\" title=\"Salesforce, Inc.\">CRM</a></span>) surged 11% after the CRM applications provider submitted a better than expected earnings sheet (in terms of revenue) for the third fiscal quarter. Salesforce beat top line estimates by a wide margin and is</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161221488/image_2161221488.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742868-salesforce-is-fairly-valued-now-rating-downgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 14:23:14"}, {"id": "4742830", "title": "The Stock Market Has Entered The Danger Zone", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/637778526/image_637778526.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Warning Danger Zone red signage in forest.\" data-id=\"637778526\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1405px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/637778526/image_637778526.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/637778526/image_637778526.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/637778526/image_637778526.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/637778526/image_637778526.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/637778526/image_637778526.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/637778526/image_637778526.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/637778526/image_637778526.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/637778526/image_637778526.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">junce</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The stock market has reached one of those moments when <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742300-most-expensive-stock-market-ever\">valuations</a> and mechanics have reached dangerous levels. The last time this happened was in July, when implied corre